node.title: NSW records 10 more Omicron COVID-19 cases as total number reaches 25
node.alt: A woman wearing protective gear stands next to a car
node.description: NSW records 10 new cases of the Omicron COVID-19 variant, with nine of the infections connected to a cluster involving a Sydney climbing gym and two schools.
node.content:
["NSW has recorded 10 new cases of the Omicron COVID-19 variant, with nine of the infections connected to a cluster involving a Sydney climbing gym and two schools.", "The state\u00a0has now recorded 25 cases of the Omicron COVID variant \u2014\u00a014 locally acquired\u00a0and 11 from overseas or on international flights.", "The outbreak of cases connected to\u00a0Regents Park Christian School and\u00a0Sydney Indoor Climbing Gym at Villawood in Sydney's south-west\u00a0spread to\u00a0St Peter Chanel Catholic Primary School.", "All year three and year four students and teachers at St Peter Chanel Catholic Primary School have been deemed close contacts and asked to self-isolate.", "A confirmed case in the ACT has also been linked to the\u00a0climbing gym.", "Anyone who was at the climbing gym on Saturday, November 27, between 9am and 4:30pm is considered a close contact and must get tested and isolate for seven days.\u00a0", "NSW Health said to date, none of these cases had been admitted to hospital for treatment.", "US health officials have said they're encouraged by early data suggesting the Omicron variant may be less dangerous than the\u00a0Delta strain.", "The strain was first recorded in South Africa and has become the dominant variant there, but hospitalisation rates have not increased alarmingly.", "America's Chief Medical Adviser, Anthony Fauci, said he was\u00a0optimistic, but more information was needed.", "\"Thus far, it does not look like there\u2019s a great degree of severity to it,\" he said.\u00a0", "\"But we have really got to be careful before we make any determinations that it is less severe comparable to Delta. But thus far the signals are a bit encouraging regarding the severity.\"", "Several cases confirmed as the Omicron variant travelled back to NSW on flights from overseas destinations in late November.", "Anyone who has\u00a0been\u00a0in South Africa, Lesotho, Botswana, Zimbabwe, Mozambique, Namibia, Eswatini and Malawi 14 days before arriving\u00a0in NSW must go into\u00a0hotel quarantine for 14 days, irrespective of their\u00a0vaccination.", "Those who have visited\u00a0any of the eight African countries within the previous 14 days must\u00a0get tested and isolate for 14 days, and call NSW Health.", "The state\u00a0recorded 208 new COVID-19 cases\u00a0and zero deaths in the 24 hours to 8pm last night.", "There are now 152 people in hospital due to COVID-19, 24 of whom are in intensive care.", "Across NSW, 94.6 per cent of people aged 16 and over have received a first dose of a COVID-19 vaccine, and 92.8 per cent are fully vaccinated.", "", "
Why we hear about some COVID-19 variants more than others
"]
